hmm. i just woke up a little while ago. i had a crazy ass dream. okay, it was me and that kid from wonder years. lol. and we were running around in this huuuuuuuuugeee movie set. trying to get away from this big burly guy and this little skinny mean guy who wanted to catch us. no clue why? but anyways. what happened was, they would catch us, and then we would slip away and run again. and this just kept happening over and over. and i mentioned this to the guy. i was like u know, ur just going to keep on almost getting us, and we're just gona keep on almost getting away. and he goes, yeah i know. and then he lunged at me. and i tried to shut the door on him, but have u ever tried to shut a door on someone who could make his body turn to ice??? yeah i dont get that part either. so i was like FINE forget it and opened the door for him. lol. then me and wonder years boy finally got to the roof of the place. and there was all these crazy ladders that finally led to the ground. so we get to the ground and i was like oh no my cell phone! and i started to go back up and was like oh well, my mom will understand and ill get a new one. and then i was like, besides its just a dream. and i was like oh yeah!!! its a dream!! hey i can fly!!! so i jumped up and started flying and everyone else started to too and i got like, 20ft off the ground and woke up. whats up with that shit?


but yeah. that was my dream.
